  61 |         struct layer_status  plane_status[KMB_MAX_PLANES];
  |                                         ^~~~~~~~~~~~
  drivers/gpu/drm/kmb/kmb_plane.c:162:34: error: array subscript 2 is above array bounds of 'struct layer_status[2]' [-Werror=array-bounds]
